    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, and it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new without the dealership price tag, you've found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'm happy to chat and give you the full tour!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
