    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside of a private collection. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the color pop in any light. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or wear, and every piece of switchgear operates with the tactile precision of a brand-new car. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. This single-owner gem has been exclusively garage-kept and comes with a complete, meticulously organized service history from certified technicians. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched factory wheels, every inch of this car reflects a life of obsessive care. This is a collector-grade example ready for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 47250.0,
